peirce
------

l1: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a , a ==> a $ by ax
l2: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a , a ==> ¬ a $ by ax
l3: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a , a ==> bot $ by bot_intro [l1, l2]
l4: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a , a ==> b $ by bot_elim [l3]
l5: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a ==> a → b $ by imp_right [l4]
l6: $ ((a → b) → a) , ¬ a ==> bot $ by imp_app [l5, l3]
l7: $ ((a → b) → a) ==> a $ by by_contra [l6]
l8: $ emp ==> ((a → b) → a) → a $ by imp_right [l7]
